flowchart TD
    E["GE_COMMANDS entry\n{ path, cli, risk, requirements, argv }"] --> CLI["ge CLI\nsame argv, same core"]
    E --> RT["console route\ncommandForRoute() → job sentinel"]
    RT --> P{"preflight\ncommandDoctor(requirements)"}
    P -->|fail| B["job blocked\nfailing checks listed,\nnothing spawned"]
    P -->|pass| D["daemon run\nPOST /api/tasks →\nnode tools/ge.mjs argv"]
    D -.->|daemon unreachable| F["local spawn fallback\n'Daemon unavailable' event"]
    D --> S["SSE job stream\nGET /api/ge/jobs/:id/logs\n→ JobToast, risk-labeled"]
    F --> S

